msgid "The key fits!"
msgstr "钥匙对上了！"

msgid "You don't know how to use it..."
msgstr "我不清楚怎么用这个东西..."

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookpile_large.dlg.narrator"
msgid "A pile of books."
msgstr "一堆书。"

msgid "A pile of books, taller than you."
msgstr "一堆书，比你还高。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookpile_massive.dlg.narrator"
msgid "A pile of books."
msgstr "一堆书。"

msgid "A massive pile of books. If they fell on you, it would hurt."
msgstr "一大堆书。如果它们倒下来，会伤到你的。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookpile_small.dlg.narrator"
msgid "A pile of books."
msgstr "一堆书。"

msgid "A pile of books, shorter than you."
msgstr "一堆书，比你要矮。"

msgid "A bookshelf housing hundreds of books."
msgstr "书架上摆放着数百本书籍。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_3.dlg.narrator"
msgid "One of them stands out."
msgstr "其中有一本很显眼。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_3.choice"
msgid "Read a passage?"
msgstr "要看一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_3.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_3.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "I don't think you should be testing on her anymore."
msgstr "我认为你不应再在她身上实验了。"

msgid "Her powers hold potential, I wish to entertain this idea a little longer."
msgstr "她的力量很有潜力，我想再考虑一下。"

msgid "She's incapable of any sort of coherent thought."
msgstr "她的思维都是不连贯的。"

msgid "We're just wasting souls on her."
msgstr "我们只是在她身上浪费灵魂罢了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_5.dlg.narrator"
msgid "One of them stands out."
msgstr "其中有一本很显眼。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_5.choice"
msgid "Read a passage?"
msgstr "要看一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_5.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_5.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_5.dlg.narrator"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "I don't know why I've decided to talk to you."
msgstr "我不知道我为何决定要与你谈话。"

msgid "Maybe it's because you look really pitiful."
msgstr "可能是因为你看起来真的太可怜了吧。"

msgid "You're so worthless that no matter what tests they put you through, you fail them all."
msgstr "你是那么没用，无论他们给你做什么测试，你全都失败了。"

msgid "If I had just left you alone that day. You wouldn't be wasting all of our time."
msgstr "要是那天我丢下你不管。你就不会浪费我们所有人的时间了。"

msgid "You wouldn't be wasting your own time here."
msgstr "你也不会在这浪费你自己的时间。"

msgid "Tomorrow, Glen will discontinue your tests."
msgstr "明日起，格伦会取消对你的测试。"

msgid "You better thank me. I'm the one who told him to."
msgstr "你最好感谢我。是我告诉他这么做的。"

msgid "I'm just sick of seeing you."
msgstr "我是真的很讨厌见到你。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_6.dlg.narrator"
msgid "One of them stands out."
msgstr "其中有一本很显眼。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_6.choice"
msgid "Read a passage?"
msgstr "要看一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_6.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_6.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "The 36th experiment has failed as well."
msgstr "第36次实验也失败了。"

msgid "I'm TELLING YOU, she's practically just a used tissue."
msgstr "我告诉过你了，她就是一张用过的餐巾纸罢了。"

msgid "Useless, USELESS demon. WE'RE WASTING OUR TIME!"
msgstr "没用的，没用的恶魔。我们都在浪费自己的时间！"

msgid "Calm down. I can't work when you're so noisy."
msgstr "冷静点。你这么吵的话，我就没法工作了。"

msgid "Go play with your other dolls."
msgstr "去玩你的其他玩偶吧。"

msgid "Maybe I WILL."
msgstr "呵，也许吧。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_8.dlg.narrator"
msgid "One of them stands out."
msgstr "其中有一本很显眼。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_8.choice"
msgid "Read a passage?"
msgstr "要看一段吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_8.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_bookshelf_8.choice.Read a passage?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Are you upset?"
msgstr "你很伤心吗？"

msgid "No, of course not."
msgstr "不，当然不了。"

msgid "You look like you're deep in thought."
msgstr "你看起来好像在深思。"

msgid "You are the one who did this to her, after all."
msgstr "毕竟是你把她害成这样的。"

msgid "Glen, back off."
msgstr "格伦，滚。"

msgid "Heh."
msgstr "呵。"

msgid "If I'm correct, you're getting yourself into a messy situation."
msgstr "如果我没猜错的话，你现在身处泥淖。"

msgid "I'll be fine."
msgstr "我会没事的。"

msgid "A large couch."
msgstr "一张大沙发。"

msgid "Maybe we should take a rest."
msgstr "也许我们应该休息一下。"

msgid "You just rested."
msgstr "你不是刚休息过嘛。"

msgid "In the cage."
msgstr "在笼子里。"

msgid "That wasn't rest, it was uncomfortable!"
msgstr "那能叫休息吗，那样子太不舒服了！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_couch.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "There's something inside the lamp."
msgstr "灯里有什么东西。"

msgid "Reach for it?"
msgstr "要伸进去找找吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_goldeneye.choice.Reach for it?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_MK_Library.misc_goldeneye.choice.Reach for it?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "There's a eyeball inside the lamp, but you no longer need it."
msgstr "灯里有一只眼球，但是你不再需要了。"

msgid "A reading table."
msgstr "一张读书桌。"
